Hi,
This patch fixes one memory leak in drivers/acpi/acpi_memhotplug.c
Replaces all kmalloc() calls succeeded by memset() to kzalloc() calls.
Applies cleanly to 2.6.18-rc4. Compile tested.

Patch starts here.


